{"tid":1555741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"場仗仲未完！唔好自己係度打J!","createTime":"2019-09-09T12:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T16:46:02.000Z","uid":173835,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"388d147beeba2c04b4fdcca4c20d51a362d3871b","tid":1555741,"uid":173835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"大家！<br />\n其實好多和理非係同溫層入面，身邊飛走晒藍絲，睇返自己友啲Facebook, WhatsApp.<br />\n但我想同大家講，唔好只係間中出黎行兩行（遊行），share下post咁,只係自己打J!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點：</span></span><br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>我希望和理非既朋友，唔好睇少自己！</strong></span></ins><br />\n其實我地既力量可以好大！<br />\n除左本身堅守信念，參與遊行之外。<br />\n大家仲有野係可以大大幫到依場運動！<br />\n要係工作及遊行以外的時間，盡量搵身邊所有朋友交流（WhatsApp，電話）。<br />\n令佢地中立既變到黃，唔行動既變到多啲行出黎！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><ins>那怕自己只改變到一個人，但我地二百萬人就變成四百萬人。 </ins></strong></span></span><br />\n團結就係力量，我地要人！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n以下幾個細cases可用，簡單易明，滅絕人性：<br />\n1. 大埔青年冇犯事被打爆頭-<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QyNY_WpzV1k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQyNY_WpzV1k&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2BulKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=edeb1a47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QyNY_WpzV1k</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 青年問警察良心係邊，又打爆頭-<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/D4qFJfnkoMY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FD4qFJfnkoMY&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2BulKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=e2001eb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/D4qFJfnkoMY</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 被捕少女求援被刻意踩手-<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xI91nwxNurs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxI91nwxNurs&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2BulKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=9adbc03a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xI91nwxNurs</a>"},{"pid":"85a0015fe5557dabbd54600ff92a8f4127e855a5","tid":1555741,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n914天水圍、915民陣大遊行"},{"pid":"23a989ea995a00e0c8accc4e7730074f42333a7b","tid":1555741,"uid":173835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:52:07.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"8d691ac0b5873281ad698fc58f053473f8d109af","tid":1555741,"uid":173835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:54:47.000Z","msg":"推 2/10"},{"pid":"155bdfae47b417bcb639085a2c2dd75781eab7a8","tid":1555741,"uid":173835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:55:56.000Z","msg":"推 3/10"},{"pid":"034d8b8aaa2f9db22763ef5fa4f2eaa56de266e7","tid":1555741,"uid":173835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"推 4/10"},{"pid":"b69d104c52c43778b05d77fb8efb6e0c65b53591","tid":1555741,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801a3f8acc5fe3bc6d246bbeeadf3b76a38f16c9","tid":1555741,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264a8589a0438ff570768975695a03909c82c0bf","tid":1555741,"uid":98141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl